# Changelog

## [0.4.0]
### Added
- Cosine similarity counting between vertex (they are similar if they have edges to the same vertex)

## [0.3.0]
### Added
- Functions to search for specialist in the given speciality or department

## [0.2.0]
### Added
- New pathfindings functions: `BFS`, `Modified Dijkstra` (the best path is that with the highest communication rate)
### Updates
- We updated test section - divided for test for graph structure and tests for algorithms

## [0.1.0]
### Added
- Core C implementation of the graph structure (`Graph`, `Vertex`, `Edge`).
- Algorithms in C: `most_central`, `busiest`, `best_collaborator`.
- Cython wrapper binding C structures to Python class `KnowNetGraph`.
- Pytest suite covering initialization and algorithm correctness.
- Setup configuration (`pyproject.toml`, `setup.py`) for local installation.
